<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10233</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克一大早就起床，然后向镇上走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他先去了鞋店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早上好，先生！”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51262</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要一份工作，有我能做的吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鞋匠摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“杰克，对不起！”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不需要帮手。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82682</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来，杰克去了面包店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82682</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他向面包师打招呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86214</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有我能做的工作吗？”杰克问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>面包师摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93223</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在没有，杰克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102683</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我的女儿们在帮我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102683</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克从一家店走到另一家店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是没有人需要帮手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118958</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么办......没有人需要帮手！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克慢慢往家走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他该怎么告诉妈妈这个坏消息呢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”他用力踢了一块石头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>石头弹了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀！” 一个声音叫道，“谁在踢石头？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克抬起头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个年轻的女人站在破旧的房子前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159431</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她正在采药。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起！” 杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不是故意的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我只是有点儿生气。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没关系！” 她对杰克笑了笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克也害羞地笑了笑：“我叫杰克。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我叫伊丽莎。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197948</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“告诉我，杰克，你为什么这么生气？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>